{"TopicId":209432,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Language","CreatedByName":"Silly Goose","CreatedById":222576,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-20T06:01:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Silly Goose","CreatedById":222576,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-20T06:01:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello i can\u0027t change language, even when i press English within steam before starting the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEverything i can find online is that it has to do with the language file, if so where can i download the latest version?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo annoying i payed almost 60 euro and can\u0027t even change language within the game itself.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am already thinking about a refund as this ridiculous i should be able to change language within the settings menu.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-20T06:07:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forum, I think we can help with your issue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn steam you just need to right click on KSP, select properties and then the language tab:\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002252.75\u0022 height=\u0022633\u0022 style=\u0022width:800px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022bgTqmlC.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/bgTqmlC.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Silly Goose","CreatedById":222576,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-20T06:08:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224165827\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209432\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660975645\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022James Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, James Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forum, I think we can help with your issue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn steam you just need to right click on KSP, select properties and then the language tab:\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/bgTqmlC.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022bgTqmlC.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002252.75\u0022 height=\u0022633\u0022 style=\u0022width:800px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/bgTqmlC.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is exactly what i did, but to no avail i\u0027m stuck in the Russian language.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-20T06:18:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224165828\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209432\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660975727\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222576\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Silly Goose\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Silly Goose said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is exactly what i did, but to no avail i\u0027m stuck in the Russian language.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm, sounds like you may have a deeper issue, I just switched my language from English to Russian and back and everything is working normally for me. Have you tried verifying the KSP game files?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Silly Goose","CreatedById":222576,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-20T06:23:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224165830\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209432\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660976283\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022James Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, James Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm, sounds like you may have a deeper issue, I just switched my language from English to Russian and back and everything is working normally for me. Have you tried verifying the KSP game files?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have reinstalled the game multiple times. Still not working .\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-20T06:29:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224165831\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209432\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660976590\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222576\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Silly Goose\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Silly Goose said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have reinstalled the game multiple times. Still not working .\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSteam has a function that will directly compare the files in your install to the current version. \u003Ca href=\u0022https://help.steampowered.com/en/faqs/view/0C48-FCBD-DA71-93EB\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESee if this process does anything\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Silly Goose","CreatedById":222576,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-20T06:44:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224165833\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209432\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660976965\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022James Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, James Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSteam has a function that will directly compare the files in your install to the current version. \u003Ca href=\u0022https://help.steampowered.com/en/faqs/view/0C48-FCBD-DA71-93EB\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESee if this process does anything\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNope still not working it is saying all files successfully validated.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-20T06:51:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224165836\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209432\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660977882\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222576\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Silly Goose\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Silly Goose said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNope still not working it is saying all files successfully validated.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen you select another language in steam do you see any progress on the update?\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002251.63\u0022 height=\u0022619\u0022 style=\u0022width:800px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022B9ab3yD.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/B9ab3yD.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Silly Goose","CreatedById":222576,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-20T06:59:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224165837\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209432\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660978282\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022James Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, James Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen you select another language in steam do you see any progress on the update?\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/B9ab3yD.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022B9ab3yD.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002251.63\u0022 height=\u0022619\u0022 style=\u0022width:800px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/B9ab3yD.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not doing anything. I have tried doing this. Why isn\u0027t it just an option within the game itself why does it has to be a struggle like this? I\u0027m just going to get a refund as its too much for a 60 euro game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen paying 60 for a game you don\u0027t want this kind of annoyance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-20T07:09:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224165839\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209432\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660978765\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222576\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Silly Goose\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Silly Goose said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not doing anything. I have tried doing this. Why isn\u0027t it just an option within the game itself why does it has to be a struggle like this? I\u0027m just going to get a refund as its too much for a 60 euro game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m really sorry about this, you seem to have come across a very uncommon problem. Selecting a new language should prompt steam to update your game files so I think something is definitely broken here and I have exhausted my knowledge so please consider \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.kerbalspaceprogram.com/support\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Eemailing KSP support\u003C/a\u003E about this and include a link to this thread to prevent duplicate troubleshooting efforts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Silly Goose","CreatedById":222576,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-20T07:15:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224165841\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209432\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660979383\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022James Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, James Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m really sorry about this, you seem to have come across a very uncommon problem. Selecting a new language should prompt steam to update your game files so I think something is definitely broken here and I have exhausted my knowledge so please consider \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.kerbalspaceprogram.com/support\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Eemailing KSP support\u003C/a\u003E about this and include a link to this thread to prevent duplicate troubleshooting efforts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUncommon? i have seen lots of people since 2017 with this problem. But it doesn\u0027t matter anymore as i have requested my refund through steam.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI will wait until KSP2 gets released, hoping it will have the option to change language.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks anyways.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}